		&lt;h3&gt;Times of India News Article&lt;/h3&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;COIMBATORE: A hospital in Coimbatore has removed what could be the world’s heaviest ovarian cancer tumour from a 46-year-old woman from Ooty.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;a href=&quot;https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/coimbatore/coimbatore-hospital-removes-worlds-heaviest-ovarian-cancer-tumour/articleshow/66181579.cms&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Click To Read Full Article&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6&quot;&gt;
		&lt;h3&gt;Asia Book of Records News Article&lt;/h3&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Dr. K. Senthil Kumar Karuppusamy (born on May 19, 1970) of Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India, along with 6 Doctors Team, have successfully removed,...&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.asiabookofrecords.com/indian-team-of-doctors-removed-the-world-heaviest-tumor-through-surgery/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Click To Read Full Article&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;row&quot;&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6&quot;&gt;
		&lt;h3&gt;Wonder Book of Record News Article&lt;/h3&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Medical profession is very sensitive and intellectual where human life is at risk. A successful effort of a doctor can save a life. Due to that, a doctor is known as 2nd God.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;a href=&quot;http://wonderbookofrecord.com/indian-team-of-doctors-set-world-record-by-removing-the-world-heaviest-tumor-through-surgery/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Click To Read Full Article&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;div class=&quot;col-md-6&quot;&gt;
		&lt;h3&gt;Khaleej Times News Article&lt;/h3&gt;
		&lt;p&gt;Doctors in India removed an ovarian tumour weighing 33.5 kg from a woman&#039;s body. Vasantha from Ooty noticed her stomach growing in size but ignored it as she did not feel any pain or discomfort initially.&lt;/p&gt;
		&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.khaleejtimes.com/international/india/Doctors-in-India-remove-33.5kg-tumour-from-womans-bod&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Click To Read Full Article&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
